# {{appName}}

A Lumora mobile-first Flutter application using {{adapter}} state management.

## Quick Start

### 1. Install Dependencies

```bash
# Install Node.js dependencies
npm install

# Install Flutter dependencies
cd mobile
flutter pub get
cd ..
```

### 2. Start Development

```bash
# Terminal 1: Start the dev proxy
cd ../../tools/dev-proxy
npm start

# Terminal 2: Watch TSX files and generate schemas
npm run dev

# Terminal 3: Run Flutter app
cd mobile
flutter run
```

### 3. Connect Device

1. Scan the QR code from the dev-proxy terminal
2. Your Flutter app will connect automatically
3. Edit `web/src/App.tsx` to see live updates

