## State Management

This project uses **{{adapter}}** for state management.

{{#if_bloc}}
### Bloc Pattern

- Events: Define user actions
- States: Define UI states
- Bloc: Business logic and state transitions

Learn more: https://bloclibrary.dev/
{{/if_bloc}}

{{#if_riverpod}}
### Riverpod Pattern

- Providers: Expose state and business logic
- ConsumerWidget: React to state changes
- StateNotifier: Manage complex state

Learn more: https://riverpod.dev/
{{/if_riverpod}}

{{#if_provider}}
### Provider Pattern

- ChangeNotifier: Manage state
- ChangeNotifierProvider: Provide state to widgets
- Consumer: Listen to state changes

Learn more: https://pub.dev/packages/provider
{{/if_provider}}

{{#if_getx}}
### GetX Pattern

- Controllers: Manage state and logic
- GetX/Obx: Reactive widgets
- Get.to(): Navigation

Learn more: https://pub.dev/packages/get
{{/if_getx}}

